<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />昨天真是謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧有你，<delay8 />我才能成功收到
聖誕老人的禮物，<delay8 />真是幫了我大忙啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收到的聖誕節玩具<delay8 />感覺也挺棒的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一個不錯的禮物啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">謝謝你<delay8 />昨天幫我
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將聖誕老人的禮物送來！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收到禮物的感覺<delay8 />果然很棒啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到那是為了我而準備的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />眼淚感覺就要奪眶而出啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，昨天真是謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從你那交換得來的禮物，<delay20 />
我會好好珍惜的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的交換禮物<delay8 />真是開心啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得我送的禮物怎麼樣啊？<delay frames="40" />
如果你能滿意那就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是我在思考許久後選的禮物，<delay8 />
我自認為有依照<delay8 />
你的喜好來進行挑選喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">明明昨天是平安夜，<delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而你卻要忙著
幫忙聖誕老人<delay8 />還有跟我交換禮物，<delay8 />
感覺有點對不起你啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />多虧有你的努力，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我度過了<delay8 />至今為止
最棒的平安夜喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧昨天從聖誕老人和<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />那收到禮物，<delay20 />
我度過了一個很棒的平安夜喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />雖說是聖誕老人的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但那也是你幫忙送來的就是了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是聖誕節喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話雖如此，<delay8 />也沒什麼特別的事情。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正<delay8 />就一如往常！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay20 />你都什麼時候吃聖誕蛋糕？
是平安夜？<delay20 />還是聖誕節當天？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />兩天都吃？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />哪天都沒差啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的話，<delay8 />只要是喜歡的東西，
我天天都想吃！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>